name: Anais Nin - I must be a mermaid...
description:
The first of hopefully many Anais Nin stickers for Bookish, this one reads:

"I must be a mermaid... I have no fear of depths and a great fear of shallow living."

It is vinyl, and can survive all kinds of weather while stuck to your car, bike, or wherever you decide to put it.

It measures 1.25" x 8.5" and has white text on a black background.

name: Henry David Thoreau Sticker Set
description:
Buy two stickers, save some money!

Sticker One:

"All good things are wild and free."

Sticker Two:

"What's the use of a fine house if you haven't got a tolerable planet to put it on?"

Each stickers measures 1.5" x 8.5" and has white text on a black background.

They are vinyl, and can survive all kinds of weather while stuck to your car, bike, or wherever you decide to put them.

name: Arrested Development - There's always money in the banana stand
description:
"There's always money in the banana stand."

Alright Mr. Manager (or Ms...) here is the sticker you've been asking for. Any fan of Arrested Development can feel special showing off this sticker. A good reminder for all...

It is vinyl, and can survive all kinds of weather while stuck to your car, bike, or wherever you decide to put it.

It measures 1.5" x 8.5" and has black text on a white background.

name: Doctor Who - My other car is a Tardis
description:
A Doctor Who sticker!

It states: "My other car is a Tardis."

This sticker is 1.5" x 8.5" with white text on a black background.

It is vinyl, and can survive all kinds of weather while stuck to your car, bike, or wherever you decide to put it.

name: Charles Bukowski Vinyl Sticker Set
description:
Three Charles Bukowski stickers!

Sticker One:

"I'd rather be reading Bukowski." (measures 1" x 8.5")

Sticker Two:

"I wanted the whole world or nothing." (measures 1.5" x 8.5")

Sticker Three:

"I don't hate people, I just feel better when they aren't around" (measures 1.5" x 8.5")

They are vinyl, and can survive all kinds of weather while stuck to your car, bike, or wherever you decide to put them.

All three stickers are black and white.
